<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_kpw_mdt_qt">
  <title>Using the Command Line Interface</title>
  <conbody>
    <p><indexterm>command line interface<indexterm>using</indexterm></indexterm>Call the <ph
        conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/> command
      line interface from the following location:</p>
    <p>
      <codeblock>$SDC_DIST/bin/</codeblock>
    </p>
    <p>Use the following command as the base for all CLI
      commands:<codeblock>$SDC_DIST/bin/streamsets cli \
(-U &lt;sdcURL> | --url &lt;sdcURL>) \
[(-a &lt;sdcAuthType> | --auth-type &lt;sdcAuthType>)] \
[(-u &lt;sdcUser> | --user &lt;sdcUser>)] \
[(-p &lt;sdcPassword> | --password &lt;sdcPassword>)] \
&lt;command> [&lt;args>] </codeblock></p>
    <p>The following table describes the options for the basic command:<table frame="all" rowsep="1"
        colsep="1" id="table_apy_55t_qt">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.5*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3.5*"/>
          <thead>
            <row>
              <entry>Option</entry>
              <entry>Description</entry>
            </row>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry>-U &lt;sdcURL> <p>or</p>--url &lt;sdcURL></entry>
              <entry>URL of the <ph
                  conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>.
                  <p>The default URL is <codeph>http://localhost:18630/</codeph>.</p></entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>-a &lt;sdcAuthType><p>or</p>--auth-type &lt;sdcAuthType></entry>
              <entry>Optional. HTTP authentication type used by the <ph
                  conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>.
              </entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>-u &lt;sdcUser><p>or</p><p>--user &lt;sdcUser></p></entry>
              <entry>Optional. User name to use to log in. The roles assigned to the user account
                determine the tasks that you can perform.<p>If you omit this option, the <ph
                    conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"
                  /> allows admin access.</p></entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>-p &lt;sdcPassword><p>or</p><p>--password &lt;sdcPassword></p></entry>
              <entry>Optional. Required when you enter a user name. Password for the user
                account.</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>&lt;command> </entry>
              <entry>Required. Command to perform.</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>&lt;args></entry>
              <entry>Optional. Include arguments and options as needed.</entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table></p>
  </conbody>
</concept>
